Title: Suu Kyi to discuss frozen dam project in China
Content: Myanmar’s de facto leader Aung San Suu Kyi left for a high-profile trip to China on Wednesday to discuss the fate of a jointly built dam and hydroelectric plant that Myanmar put on hold amid question
Author: AP
